---
// src/pages/reviews/galaxy-s26-review.astro
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Samsung Galaxy S26 Review 2026 - First Look | ReviewCloud"
  description="Read our Samsung Galaxy S26 review. First look at Samsung's latest flagship phone with improved camera, AI features, and performance."
  image="/images/galaxy-s26.jpg"
  article={true}
  publishedTime="2026-03-06"
  author="ReviewCloud"
>
  <article class="review">
    <header class="review-header">
      <span class="category">Samsung</span>
      <h1>Samsung Galaxy S26 Review: What's New in 2026</h1>
      <div class="meta">
        <span>By ReviewCloud</span>
        <span>•</span>
        <span>March 6, 2026</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="toc">
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>The Samsung Galaxy S26 is here! We've got the device in for review. Here's our first look at Samsung's latest flagship.</p>
    </div>

    <section>
      <h2>Key Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Latest Snapdragon or Exynos processor</li>
        <li>Improved camera system</li>
        <li>Galaxy AI features</li>
        <li>All-day battery life</li>
        <li>Premium design with new color options</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Camera</h2>
      <p>The S26 Ultra doesn't use a periscope zoom lens - here's why that matters for photography enthusiasts. The main camera has been upgraded with a larger sensor for better low-light performance.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Performance</h2>
      <p>Powered by the latest processor, the Galaxy S26 delivers blazing-fast performance for gaming, multitasking, and AI tasks.</p>
    </section>

    <div class="buy-links">
      <h3>Where to Buy</h3>
      <a href="https://www.amazon.com/s?k=Samsung+Galaxy+S26&tag=rc0440-20" class="buy-btn" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">
        Check Prices on Amazon
      </a>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .review { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem; background: white; }
  .review-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .category { background: #667eea; color: white; padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.875rem; }
  .review-header h1 { font-size: 1.75rem; margin: 1rem 0; }
  .meta { color: #666; display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; justify-content: center; }
  .toc { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  section { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  section h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #333; }
  ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
  li { margin: 0.5rem 0; color: #555; }
  .buy-links { text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem; padding: 2rem; background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 12px; }
  .buy-btn { display: inline-block; padding: 1rem 3rem; background: #ff9900; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; }
</style>
